      prompt: `<div>f(x) = (x &minus; a)(x &minus; b)<br>The function f is defined by the given equation, where a and b are integer constants. If f(32) &gt; 0, f(35) &lt; 0, and f(38) &gt; 0, which of the following could be the value of a + b?</div>`,
