      prompt: `<div>26z<sup>18</sup> + bz<sup>9</sup> + 70<br>In the given expression, b is a positive integer. If qz<sup>9</sup> + r is a factor of the expression, where q and r are positive integers, what is the greatest possible value of b?</div>`,
